类 PortLocationType

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.car.PortLocationType

  • public final class PortLocationType
extends java.lang.Object
    Used by INFO_FUEL_DOOR_LOCATION/INFO_CHARGE_PORT_LOCATION to enumerate fuel door or ev port location. Use getProperty and setProperty in CarPropertyManager to set and get this VHAL property.
